{"tid":252620,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得呀媽煮嘅餸最好食","createTime":"2017-05-21T18:09:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T03:23:53.000Z","uid":55564,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"29e15235df0bab624548f2c499a0225e0d7b9628","tid":252620,"uid":55564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:09:33.000Z","msg":"以前小學想餐餐都食m記 唔想番屋企食<br />\n以前中學想餐餐同fd底同學食飯 唔想番歸食<br />\n以前大學想餐餐去打邊爐食放題 唔想番歸食<br />\n果陣老媽子成日都問我番唔番屋企食飯<br />\n我心諗又係食果d 不如出街搵fd食飯算<br />\n<br />\n宜家打工日日冇得番屋企食<br />\n老媽子又日日搵fd打麻雀唔煮飯<br />\n就開始好掛住住家飯<br />\n以最便宜最少味精最新鮮食材<br />\n煮出最好溫馨嘅餸菜<br />\n成日都出街食 發覺來來去去咪又係食果d<br />\n<br />\n同呀媽食飯真係人生一大樂事"},{"pid":"8249e6a7714d7eac391956d4b7d35a93f8310ed7","tid":252620,"uid":10044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:10:04.000Z","msg":"人大先識珍惜"},{"pid":"3284a93932384dc78c3ad712a78cbaea9370579f","tid":252620,"uid":77189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:12:55.000Z","msg":"覺<br />\n依世都無機會再食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人總係要失去先知道曾經擁有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31ce844859265e3355999612f459461fa3257f7","tid":252620,"uid":19095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:17:11.000Z","msg":"好掛住嫲嫲住嘅飯 <br />\n雖然呀媽都好食<br />\n係大左先識珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c49d2e6217faa5289d77940dd1e3446acb8913","tid":252620,"uid":55564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人大先識珍惜</blockquote><br />\n人大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2853ab72efd521e7cb4bb4085684b8caa9fae929","tid":252620,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:23:05.000Z","msg":"我都好掛住媽咪煮既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmo